Usage: swapSignal [-help] [[-from <{nameList}> -to <{nameList}>] | -circle_offset <int>]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-circle_offset <int>   # specifies the offset value to swap bump in circle.
                       # It's required to be positive and less than the number
                       # of the selected bumps. (int, optional)
-from <{nameList}>     # bump names swap from (string, optional)
-to <{nameList}>       # bump names swap to (string, optional)